##  Pipe Network Testnet Node Installation Guide (Ubuntu 24.04).

| Resource    | Requirement |
| ----------- | ----------- |
| CPU         | 4 Cores     |
| RAM         | 16 GB       |
| Storage     | 100 GB SSD  |
| Internet    | 1 Gbps      |
| Last Update | 11-05-2025  |


### 1. Stop Devnet Node (if previously installed):
```
sudo systemctl stop pop.service
sudo systemctl disable pop.service
```
